        "\n",
        "### Parameter Estimation: Maximum Likelihood\n",
        "\n",
        "Parameters in ETS models — the smoothing parameters $\\alpha$, $\\beta$, $\\gamma$, $\\phi$ and the initial states — are estimated by **maximum likelihood**. Given a model specification, the one-step-ahead forecast errors $e_t = y_t - \\hat{y}_{t|t-1}$ are computed recursively. Under the assumption of Gaussian errors, the log-likelihood is:\n",
