        "$$\\ell(\\theta) = -\\frac{T}{2}\\log(2\\pi) - \\frac{T}{2}\\log\\hat{\\sigma}^2 - \\frac{1}{2\\hat{\\sigma}^2}\\sum_{t=1}^T e_t^2$$\n",
